We are seeking to appoint a Research Scientist to join the Statistics and Toxicology Section in our Research Division to work on a variety of research and review projects undertaken by the team.  This will be a permanent post based in our Edinburgh office. The post holder will provide effective application of statistical ideas to help give valid answers to substantive scientific questions, within practical constraints of time and budget. 

